ement/feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feOffset\"><code>&lt;feOffset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTile\"><code>&lt;feTile&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face\"><code>&lt;font-face&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-format\"><code>&lt;font-face-format&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</s