ref=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section></div>\n\n<p>O elemento&nbsp;<code>filter</code>&nbsp;fornece um recipiente para operações de um filtro atômico . Isso nunca será renderizado diretamente. Um filtro é referenciado pela utilização do atributo <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/filter\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">filter (en-US)</a></code> com destino de um elemento SVG.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"Contexto de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">Categorias</th><td>Nenhum</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conteúdo permitido</th><td>Qualquer número dos seguintes elementos, em qualquer ordem:<br><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element#descriptive_elements\">Elementos descritivos</a><br><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element#filter_primitive_elements\">Elementos de filtro primitivo</a><br><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animate&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos_globais","title":"Atributos globais","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/SVG/Attribute#core\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute#Core\">Atributos principais</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/SVG/Attribute#presentation\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute#Presentation\">Atributos de apresentação</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/SVG/Attribute#xlink\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute#XLink\">Atributos XLink</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/class\">class</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style\">style</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/externalResourcesRequired\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">externalResourcesRequired</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos_específicos","title":"Atributos específicos","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/x\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">x (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/y\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">y (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/width\">width</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/height\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">height (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/filterRes\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">filterRes (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/filterUnits\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">filterUnits (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/primitiveUnits\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">primitiveUnits (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/xlink:href\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">xlink:href (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interface_dom","title":"Interface DOM","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento implementa a interface do <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/DOM/SVGFilterElement\" title=\"en/DOM/SVGFilterElement\">SVGFilterElement</a></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Recurso</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Chrome</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Opera</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>3.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE&nbsp;Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>9.5</td>\n   <td>3.0[1]</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p id=\"compatWebkit\">[1] Existem&nbsp;<a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=26389\" rel=\" noopener\">alguns problemas pendentes</a>&nbsp;em navegadores Webkit.</p>\n\n<p>A tabela é baseada <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/SVG/Compatibility_sources\" title=\"en/SVG/Compatibility sources\">nessas fontes</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feBlend\"><code>&lt;feBlend&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feColorMatrix\"><code>&lt;feColorMatrix&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feComponentTransfer\"><code>&lt;feComponentTransfer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feComposite\"><code>&lt;feComposite&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feDiffuseLighting\"><code>&lt;feDiffuseLighting&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feDisplacementMap\"><code>&lt;feDisplacementMap&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feFlood\"><code>&lt;feFlood&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feGaussianBlur\"><code>&lt;feGaussianBlur&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feImage\"><code>&lt;feImage&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMerge\"><code>&lt;feMerge&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feOffset\"><code>&lt;feOffset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTile\"><code>&lt;feTile&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects\" title=\"en/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects\">Tutorial SVG: Efeitos de filtros</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Contexto de uso","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Interface DOM","id":"interface_dom"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento filter fornece um recipiente para operações de um filtro atômico . Isso nunca será renderizado diretamente. Um filtro é referenciado pela utilização do atributo filter (en-US) com destino de um elemento SVG.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<filter>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<filter>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"filter","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/svg/element/filter","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/svg/element/filter/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Gráficos Vetoriais Escaláveis"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element","title":"Referência de elementos SVG"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter","title":"filter"}],"pageTitle":"filter - SVG: Gráficos Vetoriais Escaláveis | MDN","noIndexing":false}}